    <p class="sec-deck">
      A completed adult historical-fantasy trilogy set in 17th-century Spanish-occupied Sardinia. Three books, voice-forward, multi-POV with register shifts. Published in Italian by Acheron Books; in French by Hikaya. Italian audio with Audible. <strong>English-language rights worldwide: available.</strong>
